title: The Chaff
description: In an effort to get Teen Titan Go! canceled, Control Freak shows off some deleted scenes.

title: Portal hacia Helen
description: Craig hace una conexión a larga distancia con un niño que ama el Arroyo tanto como él.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Hurricane Chata
description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

title: Fashion Forward
description: When the Fashionistas launch a new line of brainwashing clothing, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop the fashion trend before it's too late.

title: Planet X
description: When Rad returns to his home planet, he learns a shocking truth about alien society.

title: The Bus
description: When Rocky suggests the Elmore Junior High kids skip school, the bus is boarded by criminals, who seem to want to teach them the importance of school attendance. The masked culprits are clearly the children's parents faking a heist to teach them a lesson. But when the police get involved for real, it becomes clear the parents aren't the ones pulling the strings.

title: #LosConejosMágicos
description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: And Then There Was Ben
description: Professor Paradox unites the good Bens from across all dimensions to take on Vilgax, Eon, and the evil Bens in the ultimate showdown!

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: License to Drill
description: Mega Man teams up with Bert Wily to take down Drill Man, whose plan to construct hundreds of drill shaped high rises has put Silicon City in both aesthetic and physical danger!

title: The Kindergarten Kid
description: Steven and the Gems deal with a monster problem.

title: Fistfull of  Balloons
description: When Vic gets double-crossed during a water balloon fight, he goes on a revenge mission to find out who was responsible.

title: Telephonies/Tough Love
description: Telephonies: The Gangreen Gang gets hold of the Powerpuff Girls' Hotline and makes crank calls sending the Powerpuff Girls on a wild goose chases all over town./Tough Love: Everyone in Townsville loves the Powerpuff Girls! But the citizens have a sudden change of heart when Him sends out an evil gas turning the entire town against their favorite superheroes.

title: Little Elvis
description: The Titans team up with Shazam in order to defeat the evil Mr. Mind.

title: Memory Part 2
description: Windlbade and Bumblebee are attacked by Decepticons and she regains his trust.

title: Prankless
description: The guys want to win a prank war with a rival park.

title: San Diego Comic-Con Official Steven Universe Panel
description: Steven Universe creator Rebecca Sugar, Estelle, DeeDee Magno Hall, and Michaela Dietz discuss Steven Universe and its upcoming movie in this San Diego Comic-Con panel, hosted by Shelby Rabara.

title: Puff Paint
description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: Suerte
description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

title: Let's Team Up Because We Aren't Bad Friends
description: The Warriors fear that they've been ignoring their pals, so they team up with Witchy Simone and Noville for a BIG MISSION, only to discover that their friends aren't into it anymore.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: #MisgivingTree
description: Jessica Cruz and Pam Isley bond over protecting an ancient tree from being cut down. Neither of them realizes who the other's alter ego is, or the lengths to which they'll go to protect what's important.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: Fathers and Friends/Midsummer Nightmare
description: Midsummer Nightmare: Drago and the other AO Bakugan face an unseen threat with earth shattering power only to be left wondering if it was all a dream./Father's and Fiends: Osamu Kazami comes to take his son Shun back home and finds a defiance he hadn't counted on.

title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.

title: Ace of Squares
description: Craig vows to make the game of Four Square fun again by challenging its most dominant player!

title: Mr. Gus Moves Out
description: When a fed-up Mr. Gus moves out of the RV, Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve work together to get him back.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: Loteria
description: Cuando Vic hace trampa en un juego de mesa encantado, los malvados personajes cobran vida, y V y V son los responsables de averiguar cómo volver a ponerlos en el juego.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Stratified/Maze Daze
description: Stratified: The AO embark on a mission into the mysterious labyrinth world of Vestroia to find Strata the Hunter and free the Bakugan he has imprisoned./Maze Daze: Lost in the maze of Vestroia the AO encounter powerful forces that seem to be struggling for control over the alien landscape.

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: Fleas Help Me
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang help their K9 pal, Charlie Burgers, get rid of his flea infestation.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever/Just Desserts
description: The Powerpuff Girls Best Rainy Day Adventure Ever: It's raining in Townsville and there is no crime or villainy afoot. So the girls must stay inside and come up with their very own Powerpuff adventure./Just Desserts: The Smith Family is back and they want revenge. Harold, Maryanne and the kids become a super villain team and make it their goal to destroy the perfect Powerpuff family.

title: Rise and Shine
description: A glimpse at the wild, secret adventures Clarence undertakes each day before the rest of us, and the sun, get up.

title: El Relopulpo
description: En una pacífica ciudad costera, Ben no solo debe enfrentarse a Vapor Smythe -su arcaico antagonista- y a su última creación, el Relopulpo... isino que también debe enfrentarse a su temor más profundo y oscuro: los calamares!

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: Campeon del Cuadro
description: iCraig promete hacer que el juego de Cuatro Cuadros vuelva a ser divertido cuando desafía a su jugador más experto!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: La Super Increible Aventura en Balsa
description: Unikitty y Hawkodile están "perdidos en el mar," varados en una balsa juntos. Hawkodile ve esto como una oportunidad para mostrarle a Unikitty que está preparado para cualquier cosa con sus habilidades de experto en supervivencia, pero para su sorpresa, todos sus planes fracasan, mientras que la tonta postura de Unikitty de "todo saldrá bien, vamos a divertirnos" está funcionando de una manera genial. ¿Será Hawkodile capaz de soltar su exceso de preparación para salvarlos a ambos, o acaso la diversión caprichosa de Unikitty será su perdición?

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Hot to the Touch
description: Finn goes on a quest to prove Flame Princess isn't really evil.

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: Gem Hunt
description: Steven and Connie track a Gem monster through the wilderness but its tracks lead them to mystery.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: Supernatural Adventures in Babysitting
description: Stargirl has to enlist Constantine's help when Klarion the Witch Boy takes the place of the boy she's supposed to be babysitting.

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Fire!
description: Grizz's quick thinking prevents a potential wild fire, but the praise he receives from doing so quickly goes to his head.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: Last Laugh
description: Ben's fear of clowns emerges at an unfortunate time when our heroes stumble upon a wicked circus with a psychic vampire clown named Zomobozo.

title: The Big Sleep
description: When the Professor's latest invention wreaks havoc in the house, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop it before it escapes.

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: Summer Showers
description: Jake's daughter Viola is up for a role in a play by a hot new director, Lumpy Space Princess.

title: The Babysitter
description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

title: The Tell Tale Schedulebot
description: After Blossom and Buttercup break Schedulebot, they'll do anything to keep the truth from coming out.

title: Steven Universe Love Like You Performance at San Diego Comic-Con
description: Steven Universe creator Rebecca Sugar performs "Love Like You," from the end credits of Steven Universe at San Diego Comic-Con.

title: Girls Night In Part 1
description: The Girls Night Out Crew decide to stay in and have a slumber party but an unknown alien threat descends on Jump City.

title: Doorway to Helen
description: Craig makes a long distance connection with a kid that loves the creek as much as he does.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: The Cycle
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais discover that Mr Wilson has been picking on their Dad for most of his life; ever since he humiliated Richard with a high school prank. The kids try to work Dad through it but when their efforts fail, they realize that getting back at Mr Wilson is the only way to break the cycle.

title: Steven Universe Ultimate Catch-Up Trailer
description: Take a look back on Steven's journey with this ultimate catch-up trailer!

title: Access Denied
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to go to Margaret's birthday party at an exclusive club.

title: Fractured Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bumblebee does not remember her and her mission to find the Allspark is critical.

title: School's In, Oh Bummer
description: It turns out that Vambre and Prohyas didn't graduate the Adventure Academy after all and need to go back to school earn their diplomas!

title: El silencioso
description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.

title: Truth
description: An old Plumber partner of Max's resurfaces with nefarious intentions and ends up stealing the dangerous Null Void Projector.

title: Nickname
description: When a kid wants a cool nickname, UG tells him he has to earn it in the most legendary way ever: yard work!

title: Whatever Happened to... Rippy Roo?
description: Rippy Roo visits the plaza.

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: Doctor Visit
description: Uncle Grandpa hates going to the doctor but he's overdue for an important vaccination.

title: Huracan Chata
description: Cuando V y V descubren que las emociones de Chata controlan el agua del lago, deciden sacar ventaja y comienzan su propio negocio de piscinas de olas.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: El Lider Del Ring
description: Cuando Ben tiene una racha ganadora en un videojuego, se le ocurre una idea para ganar un partido real de lucha, hasta que un luchador intimidante decide convertirlo en un verdadero desafío.

title: Framing Device/Bad Actors
description: Framing Device: When confronted by China Riot Lia learns to evolve Pegatrix after realizing the true meaning behind her filming obsession./Bad Actors: Dan tries to lie about evolving Drago and gets exposed while the team face off against Duran Dane and his unhappy Bakugan Nillious.

title: Chair
description: Unikitty finds an old, beatup recliner on the curb, but sees its inner beauty and brings it home to introduce to the gang! In a series of absurd and fun vignettes, we discover how a dirty, inanimate chair comes into each of their lives and changes them for the better. We soon learn that dear, sweet Chair was too good for this world.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.

title: Perricornio Patinador
description: Puppycorn quiere impresionar a sus amigos patinadores con sus habilidades fantásticas, el problema es que no tiene ninguna. Con la esperanza de aumentar su confianza, Unikitty y la pandilla se ponen los trajes invisibles de la Dra. Fox para ayudarlo secretamente a realizar movimientos imposibles. Pero hacen su trabajo demasiado bien y el "patinador profesional" Puppycorn está invitado a mostrar sus habilidades en una peligrosa competencia de escenas de riesgo. ¿Hasta dónde llegará la pandilla para ayudar al cachorro a realizar sus sueños inalcanzables e increíbles?

title: Back to the Moon
description: Steven and the Gems revisit the Moon Base.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.

title: Superman's Pal, Sid Sharp
description: When obnoxious reporter Sid Sharp decides that Clark Kent is getting all his stories because of his connection to Superman, Sid decides to become his own superhero to out scoop him.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: Enemy Mime
description: When the Sheriff's Dept fights a monster that copies their every move, they'll have to find a way to fight without fighting.

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Juego de mascaras
description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.

title: All Good in the Wood
description: When Suna and Ashley's science project turns into a hungry blob monster, Mega Man must team up with Wood Man to shut down the experiment gone wrong before it devours the city!

title: Riding the Storm Out
description: Ben and Gwen's camping trip is interrupted by the emotionless Weatherheads (Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o) but a malfunctioning Omnitrix firing out a mishmash of aliens may not be the forecast for success.

title: Panda's Birthday
description: For Panda's Birthday, the Bears try to help Panda meet his favorite K-Pop band, Monsta X.

title: Mini Golf Madness
description: Buttercup takes her game winning mini golf ball, in spite of ominous warnings of dire consequences.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: Dawn Before Dusk
description: Dawn Before Dusk, Part 1: The AO meet Benton Dusk discovering that their quiet little corner of the world is about to become much, much larger./Dawn Before Dusk, Part 2: Benton Dusk reveals that the AO have been indentified as persons of interest by powerful corporations including Philomena Dusk's AAAnimus.

title: Pal.0
description: When the RV's talking computer system malfunctions, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must figure out a way to stop the rogue computer and restore life in the RV back to normal.

title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: An American Benwolf in London
description: Ben and Rook are called to London England to investigate the Forever Knights' latest activities.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Brawl Bot
description: Dr. Fox is proud to unveil her new ultimate combat machine and take it into an underground scientist fighting ring. But Hawkodile's jealous of Dr. Fox's fighting bot that's supposedly a better puncher than him and declares he can beat anything it can. To prove his point, he dresses up in spare robot parts and enters himself secretly in the bot battle. With Unikitty as his fighting coach, can Hawkodile survive the tourney, prove he's tougher than a machine, and avoid the scrap yard?

title: Slumber Party
description: Clarence struggles to make a connection at an all-girls slumber party, leaving Sumo and Jeff at odds without Clarence as their "friendship buffer."

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Plane Excited
description: Clarence is all excited visit his grandma when he learns that Chad has never been on a plane. Clarence makes it his mission to help Chad get through a hectic flight.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: Inglorious Toddlers
description: Owen fears he's about to lose his BFF Noah to a gifted military school.

title: The Misunderstandings
description: Gumball has misunderstood about his date with Penny. He thought they were meeting for dinner but they were actually meeting for lunch at a Diner called Dinner. He runs to the mall but everyone he meets on the way seems to misunderstand him in a different way. Once he finally does get to the mall, it seems all his misunderstandings have caught up with him.

title: Sparkle Cadet
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP team up with an intergalactic hero named Sparkle Cadet, hoping to save the Creek from negativity.

title: King of the Zombeez
description: Frostferatu hires the Warriors to rid his castle of Zombeez when Neddy and a power mad zombie-bee queen take over.

title: The Brain Buster
description: A mysterious creature abducts Batman, Mr. Terrific, Luthor and two of the brainiest villains in the universe to put them to the test to discover who is the smartest among them.

title: Them Soviet Boys
description: In order to quickly get through their chores and karate lessons, the Titans learn how to montage

title: Candy Streets
description: LSP is robbed and faints before she can tell Finn and Jake who robbed her.

title: Bananas & Cheese
description: Duncan is determined to stop the musical duo Bananas & Cheese from coming to the daycare.

title: The K.O. Trap
description: KO, Rad, and Enid are caught in an especially devious trap.

title: La ninera
description: Vic y Val quieren colarse en un espectáculo secreto de fuegos artificiales, pero su plan se ve frustrado cuando su nueva niñera, Xochi, los supera en todo momento.

title: Steven Universe the Movie Trailer
description: Steven thinks his time defending the Earth is over, but when a new threat comes to Beach City, Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: A Real Steal/Lightning Unleashed
description: A Real Steal: Dan embarks on a solo adventure to outdo Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers and winds up having to be saved by them instead./Lightning Unleashed: Lightning uncovers the Mind Core Cell buried beneath the Earth and battles Stata the Hunter in an effort to protect its secret.

title: All Jungled Up/Outer Demons
description: All Jungled Up: Still lost in Vestroia the AO experience mind altering effects of the nearby Core Cell and come face to face with the Bakuzon monster Tiko./Outer Demons: The AO find the doorway out of Vestroia only to learn they have entered a mirror world of their own imagining created by the Core Cell.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: Glory Days
description: KO does a school report on Carol.

title: Tasty Heist
description: Richard's prepared one of the tastiest desserts ever, but he's locked it up tight until the friends have their boring dinner. This will not stand. Unikitty organizes a heist, assembling the friends as a crack team to get in, get out, and eat that tasty snack without Richard knowing. But this heist has hiccups. Can the friends take the cake?

title: Hic Hic Hooray
description: Bridgette gets the hiccups and becomes desperate to get rid of them.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 1
description: Bee, Windblade and Grimlock finally determine the location of the lost ship, the Ark.

title: The Throw Down/Brawl for It All
description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: Escape from Beyond the Cosmic
description: When Clarence accidentally breaks a local arcade game Jeff has become obsessed with, Clarence puts together his own real-life version of the game at home, encouraging Jeff to act out his fantasy in levels created exclusively by Clarence.

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: Steven Universe: Behind the Curtain Trailer
description: Get a sneak peek at the team who created Steven Universe the Movie in this trailer for a behind-the-scenes documentary.

title: Freedom Cactus
description: Clarence draws a comic for the school paper and it becomes a huge hit with the kids. When angry parents step in and censor the comic's crass humor, Clarence must stand up for his artistic vision.

title: El verdadero potencial
description: Justo cuando los ninjas piensan que han salvado el día, Lord Garmadon regresa a Ninjago, y libera a Harumi, quien lo anima a "alcanzar su verdadero potencial" conquistando lo único que siempre se interpuso en su camino, su hijo, Lloyd.

title: Quest for Knowledge
description: After a flashback where we learn the origins of the Warriors passion for Magiswords, they return to Adventure Academy where Professor Cyrus sets V and P and their former classmates on a quest to find the Legendary Knowledge Magisword.

title: Love at First Bite
description: Val crushes on a girl named Matty, who Vic is suspicious of but Val ignores his warnings. When Val goes to dinner at her house she turns into a Matlazihua and he discovers he's what's for dinner!

title: Maccadam's Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bee's memory must be coming back - they access the Hivemind and visit three different eras of Maccadam's.

title: Under Siege
description: Having learned Master Wu is the "Treacherous One," the ninja find themselves under siege at the Monastery, trying to protect Wu from the wrath of Aspheera.

title: Allspark Part 2
description: They search for clues as to the whereabouts of the Allspark and uncover another important memory!

title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

title: The Stink
description: Gumball decides to put Mr. Small's eco-friendly principles to the test but it doesn't quite go as planned. Mr. Small disappears after deciding to leave the modern world behind. But on the plus side they discover that the Great Stink-Ape of Elmore Woods is definitely not extinct.

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.

title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

title: Watchtower Tours
description: When Booster Gold starts to secretly give tours of the Watchtower to make some extra cash, he inadvertently brings in a super villain disguised as a tourist.

title: Big Bad Dreams
description: When Namagem starts using his Hypno powers to haunt Aki's dreams, our hero must face his fears in the dreamscape.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 2
description: Teletraan-X's scans reveal their old friend Grimlock, who is intent on finding the rest of his missing dinosaur friends.

title: Fractured Part 1
description: Windblade discovers Bumblebee in the desert on his own.

title: 4 a 1
description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

title: Super Amazing Raft Adventure
description: Unikitty and Hawkodile are "lost at sea", stranded on a raft together. Hawkodile sees this as an opportunity to show Unikitty that he's prepared for anything with his expertly-honed survival skills, but to his shock, all of his plans keep falling apart, while Unikitty's silly "it'll all work out, let's have fun" approach is somehow working great! Will Hawkodile manage to let go of his overpreparedness to save them both, or will Unikitty whimsical fun be their doom?

title: Mystery, Incorporeal
description: An old enemy emerges while Ben and Rook visit Kevin and Gwen at college.

title: Never Trust a Human
description: A flashback episode tells the story of Young Wu and Young Garmadon meeting Aspheera and teaching her the secrets of Spinjitzu.

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Save Mojo/Substitute Creature
description: Save Mojo: An animal activist group sets out to protect Mojo, ensuring that he can behave like the naturally evil monkey that he is./Substitute Creature: A substitute teacher comes to Pokey Oaks and the girls are sure that this creature teacher is up to no good.

title: #FromBatToWorse
description: Having just moved to the boring Metropolis suburbs, Batgirl is thrilled when she intercepts a call from Batman asking for help. But before she can stop a visiting Gotham villain, she'll have to sneak past her dad, Police Commissioner Gordon.

title: The Quiet One
description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

title: Beta
description: Steven and Amethyst visit some friends in the country but Amethyst isn't being herself.

title: Powerless
description: The ninja rush to the NINJAGO Museum of History to recover a dangerous scroll before it falls into the hands of the Serpentine Sorceress Aspheera.

title: Atrapa la Botella
description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

title: Rad Monster Party
description: Ben and Rook enlist the help of intergalactic smuggler Rad Dudesman to fly them through the Anur System—the home of the monstrous aliens!

title: Siloed Part 2
description: Windblade manages to fight her way out when Slipstream is called away and she discovers Bee and Teletraan-X are there to help!

title: Conquest of Cuteness
description: King Snuggadoodle and the Huggaboopies invade Finn and Jake's tree house.

title: K.O. vs Fink
description: When Fink taunts KO for being a momma's boy, he grapples with newfound insecurity about it.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: Outfoxed
description: When Rufus and Reg come to swindle the town, Sheriff Mao Mao teaches them a lesson in justice.

title: Having the Timeout of Our Lives
description: Owen forms a special bond with Duncan after having loads of fun with him during their timeouts.

title: Not Impressed
description: When a Sweetypie isn't impressed with the sheriff dept's antics, our three heroes try everything to win him over.

title: The Gym
description: The Bears go to the gym and get quite the work out.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 2
description: Bee remembers an early version of Megatron where he was a gladiatorial hero, but realizes how dangerous he became.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 1
description: Windblade explains the threat of Megatron and the Decepticons to Bee.

title: Innervasion Part 2: Call the Dream Police
description: After defeating the Warbot and discovering Vilgax inside, Ben's "secret voices" only worsen and begin affecting his sleep, but once Gwen discovers a sleepwalking Ben using missing items from the campsite to create his own massive Junkbot, it is up to Ben to stop his own creation.

title: Steven Universe True Kinda Love Performance at San Diego Comic-Con
description: Steven Universe creator Rebecca Sugar and Estelle perform a new song from Steven Universe the Movie at San Diego Comic-Con.

title: Eruption Part 1
description: As the Autobots discover the Ark, they have to wake up their friends in this battle for the future.

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: Framed
description: Kevin 11 is back and out for revenge. And with the ability to shape-shift into several of Ben's alien heroes, he's been framing Ben for his crimes.

title: Had to Be There
description: So she isn't left out of inside jokes, the Titans time travel to past adventures and insert Bumblebee into their memories.

title: Steven vs. Amethyst
description: Steven and Amethyst get competitive while training with Pearl.

title: In the Garden of Good and Eddie
description: When the girls try a quick-fix on their neglected veggie garden, they are left with a giant, mooching tomato worm they must care for.

title: Not Without My Fudgy Lumps
description: Noah tries to rescue the chocolates Owen forgot outside.

title: The Ring Leader
description: While winning big on a Sumo Slammers video game, Ben gets the idea to win a wrestling match for real until an intimidating wrestler named Iron Kyle decides to make it a true challenge.

title: Fire Man in the Hole
description: While hiking on a dormant volcano, Aki sets out to retrieve Ashley's lost camera and, as Mega Man, to stop Fire Man from setting off an eruption!

title: Him Diddle Riddle
description: The Powerpuff Girls must solve a series of Him's riddles to keep the Professor from having to pay.

title: The Journey Part 1
description: Bee accesses a memory from onboard the Ark on its journey from Cybertron to Earth.

title: The Claws of the Cat
description: While taking in the sights and sounds of a Rio de Jenaro music festival, Ben bristles at Gwen's suggestion that she be his new sidekick, but when the festival is threaten by the supersonic sound waves of Lord Decibel, our hero must lean on help from some familiar faces: DJ Gpa and Gwen-Cat!

title: Home on the Run/Top Slot
description: Home on the Run: We are introduced to Shun's mysterious backstory, his relationship with his industrialist father and desire for a closer knit family./Top Slot: Dan and Shun butt heads on how best to make the AO a real team amidst growing threats including the mysterious Shargo Ronin.

title: Evergreen
description: In a distant age, the wizard Evergreen quests to save the world.

title: Trucker Hall of Fame
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to help Muscle Man get to the Big Rig Museum to spread his dad's hat's ashes.

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

title: Bottle Catch
description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

title: Shadowstriker Part 1
description: Bee doubts his fighting abilities as he continually loses in practice to Windblade.

title: The Last Kid in the Creek
description: A terrible curse leaves Craig as the only kid in the creek.

title: Kickflip McPuppycorn
description: Puppycorn wants to impress his skater friends with his sweet skills, except he has none. Hoping to boost his confidence, Unikitty and the gang put on Dr. Fox's invisibility suits to secretly help him pull off impossible moves! But they do their job too well and "pro skater" Puppycorn is invited to showcase his skills in a dangerous stunt competition. How far will the gang go to help the pup live out his rad pipe dreams?

title: The Ollie
description: When Darwin asks Gumball to teach him how to skate, Gumball makes sure he covers every aspect of the skating lifestyle from wearing the right gear, using the right terms and choosing the right board. But when Darwin finally gets his wheels rolling, he realizes there might be one important aspect of skating Gumball hasn't taught him.

title: Whiteout Part 1
description: Bee remembers his escape pod from the Ark crashed in the snowy Himalayas.

title: Diary
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to fix a lock on Margaret's diary before she gets back from a weekend trip.

title: The Clocktopus
description: In a peaceful coastal town, Ben must not only face the archaic antagonist Steam Smythe and his latest creation, the Clocktopus, but also his deepest, darkest fear: Squids!

title: Lickety Split
description: When a mysterious electrical storm downs the Omni-Copter at the Equator, Team Tennyson soon discovers Solar & Polar are behind it, but when Ben accidentally combines the two into a more powerful Uni-Twin, our hero must think fast if he is going to save the planet!

title: Allspark Part 1
description: Hiding from the Decepticons, Windblade use her Cityspeaker powers to search Bee's memory files.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: Eruption Part 2
description: Teletraan-X has to reboot the offline computer systems to wake up their Autobot friends and the ship while fighting the Deceptions.

title: El ultimo nino en el Arroyo
description: Por una terrible maldición, Craig se convierte en el único niño del Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: Sillon
description: Unikitty encuentra una vieja silla reclinable en la acera, pero ve su belleza interior y lo lleva a casa para mostrárselo a la pandilla. En una serie de situaciones absurdas y divertidas, descubrimos cómo una silla sucia e inanimada entra en cada una de sus vidas y las cambia para mejor. Pronto aprendemos que la querida y dulce silla era demasiado buena para este mundo.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Council of the Creek
description: The circle game wreaks havoc on the Creek, so Craig forms a council to restore order.

title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

title: The Mask of Deception
description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

title: The Vampire Strikes Back
description: Ben, Rook, and Rad Dudesman come face to face with the evil Lord Transyl, a vampire-like alien who can make anyone his loyal slave! (Introducing new Ben alien, Whampire.)

title: Shadowstriker Part 2
description: Through memory, Bee is shown some of his past triumphs, like rescuing Optimus from Shadowstriker.

title: The Extinction Event Part 1
description: Decepticons Shockwave and Shadowstriker arrive on Earth with a simple plan to find the Allspark.

title: Sabro Atraco
description: Richard preparó uno de los postres más sabrosos de todos los tiempos, pero lo cerró con llave hasta que los amigos terminen su cena aburrida. Esto no va a seguir así. Para organizar un atraco, Unikitty organiza a sus amigos como un comité de expertos para entrar, salir y comer ese sabroso bocadillo sin que Richard lo sepa. Pero este atraco tiene un traspié. ¿Podrán los amigos llevarse el pastel?

title: Duelo de globos
description: Cuando Vic es traicionado durante una guerra de globos de agua, emprende una vengativa misión para descubrir al responsable.

title: Busted Cart
description: Mordecai and Rigby bust up the cart while doing stunts and have to figure out a way to fix it.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 2
description: Slipstream and her Seekers engage in battle as our heroes trek towards the Ark.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 2
description: Bee finds himself on Velocitron with Hod Rod to have some fun but it turns into a nightmare as the Plague of Rust descends.

title: Dread on Arrival
description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: #CrushingIt
description: Diana Prince is absolutely crushing it in every single aspect of life as a student at Metropolis High, until someone shows up who threatens to throw her off her game for good.

title: #BurritoBucket
description: Babs loves her job at fast food restaurant Burrito Bucket, but her boss, who's fed up with her chronic lateness and bad case of scatterbrain, would love any excuse to fire her. When a bank robbery breaks out right across the street from work, Babs is torn between her role as a superhero and dutiful Burrito Bucket employee. Will she be able to save the day and keep her job all in the nick of time?

title: Hiccup the Volume
description: Monkey Chunks has hiccups and Biblia Tick hires the Warriors to get rid of them.

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Bao Bao's Revenge
description: When Mao Mao's old partner threatens the kingdom, his friends will need to learn about his past in order to protect the present.

title: Maccadam's Part 1
description: Bee and Windblade avoid an attack by Slipstream and Bee asks to go to Maccadam's!

title: Innervasion Part 1: Message in a Boxcar
description: As Team Tennyson prepares their boxcar for an upcoming race, Ben is hearing voices and is unable to go Upgrade to enhance his car, but once the race is interrupted by a mysterious Warbot, Ben must overcome the voices inside his head if he is to defeat the giant adversary.

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: Bubble
description: Panda becomes a germophobe and decides to live the rest of his life in a bubble.

title: Sobreviviendo A La Tormenta
description: El campamento de Ben y Gwen se ve interrumpido por los gélidos Weatherheads -Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o-, pero un Omnitrix que funciona mal y dispara un montón de extraterrestres podría no ser un pronóstico de éxito.

title: The Oni & the Dragon
description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

title: Amor a primera mordida
description: A Val le gusta una chica llamada Matty, y Vic sospecha de ella, pero Val ignora sus advertencias. Cuando Val va a su casa a cenar, ella se convierte en una Matlazihua, iy Val descubre que él es la cena!

title: Terror llegando
description: Los ninjas recurren al comisionado de la policía de Ninjago en un esfuerzo por ayudar a salvar a Lloyd y frustrar los esfuerzos de Harumi de resucitar al malvado Lord Garmadon.

title: A Split End
description: After replicating Cut Man's powers, Mega Man goes on a perfectionist spree, putting him on a collision course with Cut Man himself, whose latest stint as a hairdresser hasn't helped him overcome his own compulsions.

title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.

title: El oni y el dragon
description: Mientras que la Princesa Harumi se adapta a la vida con los ninjas, Lloyd y Jay buscan respuestas sobre las máscaras Oni, mientras que Cole y Zane intentan infiltrarse en Los Hijos de Garmadon.

title: Ancient History
description: While Aspheera pursues revenge on the "Treacherous Deceiver" who betrayed her, the ninja make a startling discovery.
